## ❌ ALWAYS: Custom Exceptions in Services

```python
from app.api.errors import NotFoundError, ValidationError

# ✅ GOOD - Use custom exceptions in services
if not assignment:
    raise NotFoundError("Assignment", str(assignment_id))

if grade_level not in range(6, 11):
    raise ValidationError("Grade level must be between 6 and 10")

# ❌ BAD - Never raise HTTPException in services
raise HTTPException(status_code=404)  # Don't do this
```

