## 🗄️ Database & Migrations

### Alembic Workflow
```bash
# 1. Create/edit model in db/models/
# 2. Import model in db/base.py
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "add lessons table"
# 3. REVIEW generated migration file
alembic upgrade head
# 4. Sync to Supabase
supabase db diff -f add_lessons
supabase db push
```

### Session Management
```python
# ✅ GOOD - Use dependency
@router.get("/")
async def get_items(db: AsyncSession = Depends(get_db)):
    result = await db.execute(select(Item))
    return result.scalars().all()

# ❌ BAD - Manual session creation
async with AsyncSessionLocal() as session:  # Don't do this
    ...
```

