### Files
- `{entity}_model.py`, `{entity}_schema.py`, `{entity}_service.py`, `{entity}_routes.py`

### Classes
- Models: `Assignment`, `User` (PascalCase)
- Schemas: `AssignmentCreate`, `AssignmentResponse` (PascalCase + suffix)
- Services: `AssignmentService` (PascalCase + Service)

### Variables
- `snake_case` for functions/variables
- `UPPER_CASE` for constants

### Database
- Tables: `assignments`, `users` (plural snake_case)
- Columns: `teacher_id`, `created_at` (snake_case)

